wdi-BX.TRF.PWKR.CD.def: Personal transfers consist of all current transfers in cash or in kind made or received by resident households to or from nonresident households. Personal transfers thus include all current transfers between resident and nonresident individuals. Data are in current U.S. dollars.
wdi-BX.TRF.PWKR.CD.name: Personal transfers, receipts
wdi-BX.TRF.PWKR.CD.source: International Monetary Fund, Balance of Payments Statistics Yearbook and data files.
